title: Typescript
text: Typescript adds static type checking to JavaScript. This is preferred over writing plain JS, as the type checker can eliminate many potential bugs at build time.

title: ESLint
text: ESLint provides static analysis for typescript code. A comprehensive ruleset is included in this project which covers react and the associated testing libraries.

title: Material UI
text: Material UI provides a library of customisable react UI components which are optimized for accessibility and responsive design.

title: React Router
text: React router is configured with 2 example routes. This sample uses code splitting to improve the performance and bundle size of the application.
